OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773090365
OL,3,CMan found guilty of rape and knowingly
OL,4,Cinfecting seven men with HIV
OL,6,FA man from Wearside has been convicted
OL,7,Fof rape and causing grievous bodily
OL,8,Fharm, after deliberately infecting men
OL,9,Fwith HIV.
OL,11,FAdam Hall, 43, previously of Donvale
OL,12,FRoad in Washington, was found guilty
OL,13,Fat Newcastle Crown Court of charges
OL,14,Frelating to the deliberate infection
OL,15,Fof seven men with HIV.
OL,17,FOf those who were infected, Hall was
OL,18,Falso found guilty of raping four of
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
