FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773090365
OL,3,CMan found guilty of rape and knowingly
OL,4,Cinfecting seven men with HIV
OL,6,FAmy Dixon of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService said: "From the point of his
OL,8,Finitial HIV diagnosis, Adam Hall was
OL,9,Fwholly aware of the risks to himself
OL,10,Fand others if he failed to adhere to
OL,11,Fhis medical treatment. Despite this,
OL,12,Fhe repeatedly pursued sexual activity
OL,13,Fwith his victims without disclosing
OL,14,Fhis HIV status.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773090365
OL,3,CMan found guilty of rape and knowingly
OL,4,Cinfecting seven men with HIV
OL,6,F"In some cases, Hall performed these
OL,7,Fsexual acts without the consent of the
OL,8,Fvictims, applying verbal or physical
OL,9,Fforce to get what he wanted. Hall
OL,10,Fprovided one of his victims with the
OL,11,Fillegal drug GHB (gamma-
OL,12,Fhydroxybutyrate) and there were times
OL,13,Fwhen he would black out and awake to
OL,14,FHall raping him.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773090365
OL,3,CMan found guilty of rape and knowingly
OL,4,Cinfecting seven men with HIV
OL,6,F"It is clear from his actions that
OL,7,FHall knew what he was doing and fully
OL,8,Fintended to cause the harmful lifelong
OL,9,Fconsequences that his victims now
OL,10,Fface. We would like to praise the
OL,11,Fbravery of these men in coming forward
OL,12,Fto provide evidence and we hope that
OL,13,Fthe conviction of Hall today provides
OL,14,Fsome measure of justice for each of
OL,15,Fthem."
OL,17,FHall was also convicted of a drugs
OL,18,Foffence and failing to unlock his
OL,19,Fphone for police.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
