PN,42508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1773090365
OL,3,CMan found guilty of rape and knowingly
OL,4,Cinfecting seven men with HIV
OL,6,FJudge Edward Bindloss thanked the jury
OL,7,Ffor their work on an "extraordinarily
OL,8,Fcomplex and troubling case", which
OL,9,Ffeatured "difficult evidence to hear."
OL,11,FHe remanded Hall in custody until
OL,12,FApril 23 when he will be sentenced.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
